data.name: Cinnamon Sugar Toast
data.quickTastyDescription: A delightful, sweet toast topped with a buttery cinnamon-sugar blend, perfect for breakfast or a snack.
detailedCookingInstructions: Toast the slices of bread until golden brown.
In a small bowl, mix the sugar and ground cinnamon together.
Spread the butter on the warm toast.
Sprinkle the cinnamon-sugar mixture evenly over the buttered toast.
